title: I Went Duck Herding For My 100K Special | UnConventional
description: In this video, Max Fosh celebrates reaching 100k subscribers by trying out duck herding, a unique and unconventional activity.
summary: Max Fosh goes duck herding for his 100k special, showcasing the quirky and unexpected side of celebrating a milestone.
style: Absurd and humorous as Max tries his hand at a bizarre activity like duck herding.
payoff: The humor comes from watching Max attempt to herd ducks, a task that seems simple but proves to be quite challenging and entertaining to watch.
